        Parameters:
        context - android context
        name - Device Name
        bluetoothDevice - Bluetooth device - Obtained through Scan Results
        hasDistoService - True, Service visible before connection: APP should connnect without pairing
        False, Service Not Visible before connection: APP should pair first and then connect
